# Database

- Schema: `server/prisma/schema.prisma`; DB URL in `server/prisma.config.ts`
- After schema changes: `db:generate` before typecheck — `./scripts/check.sh` does this automatically
- Prisma client in `server/src/db.ts` via `@prisma/adapter-pg` — import `prisma` in tRPC procedures
- Keep models aligned with the timetable domain (events, favourites)
